data.description: Come see this spacious four bedroom two and a half bath home located in the desirable neighborhood of Moss Grove Plantation. As you enter the home, you will find a generous sized study/bonus room. Moving forward you will find your large dining and a large open floor plan family room with a large kitchen adjacent to the family room.Just beyond the family room you will find the sliding glass door that leads out onto the patio and into a spacious backyard that fully enclosed utilizing a six-foot privacy fence. The kitchen has plenty of counter and cabinet space. It also has a huge pantry and a rather large stairwell storage area. This kitchen also has beautiful large granite counter tops with a tiled backsplash.    The Island has a great over hang for breakfast stools. The appliances compliment the kitchen and include a microwave, and dishwasher. Making your way to the second floor you will be greeted by an extra-large loft space. Three generous sized secondary bedrooms along with a full bath. Adjacent to the secondary bedrooms sits the generous sized master suite complete with a large walk-in closet. The master bath has a separate tub and shower with a raised double vanity. The laundry room is also located upstairs for convenience.
